(text "== Five-port external USB architecture: USB7206C hub and three source-only Type-C ports ==" (at 20.32 12.7 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 529b0644-6b1c-5de5-9564-a2b89c347863))
(text "Mu HSIO1 plus USB2_P4 is the hub upstream. Hub port 1 feeds rear-right dual-role J11 on sheet 5." (at 20.32 20.32 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid bedb99a8-47e5-5bd4-8451-599ebb668010))
(text "J22, J23, and J12 are data/source-only. TPD1S514-1 blocks forced high-voltage VBUS; compliant charger attach is a safe no-op." (at 20.32 27.94 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 1c0d3f06-4532-5a16-b766-60ad07244878))
(text "USB_PORT_5V is private to the five external ports; per-port current limiting prevents one cable fault from dropping the laptop." (at 20.32 35.56 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 0fbda446-4174-5fac-ad19-66d85a7016a8))
(text "USB7206C VBUS_DET follows supervised physical host VBUS; unused ports 5/6 are disabled by DP/DM high straps." (at 20.32 43.18 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 4b5ed32b-6566-5928-9c9b-0c93df98bb21))
(text "== Dedicated 6A-class port rail and 1.15V hub-core rail ==" (at 20.32 45.72 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid c94f6a52-a1a6-501f-9c77-a1c94d68dcc2))
